    "2869:17": "none“> 1 . 1 iha sattvamarthakriyākāritvaṃ taditarasattvalakṣaṇāyogāt |",
    "2869:18": "1 . 2 tacca kramayaugapadyābhyāṃ vyāptaṃ parasparavyavacchedalakṣaṇatvādanayoḥ |",
    "2869:19": "1 . 3 prakārāntareṇa karaṇāsambhavāt |",
    "2869:20": "1 . 4 kramayaugapadye cākṣaṇikatve na staḥ |",
    "2869:21": "1 . 5 pūrvāparakālayoravicalitaikasvabhāvasya karttṛtvākarttṛtve virūddhadharmadvayāyogāt |",
