    "2869:28": "none“> 2 . 1 tatra na tāvat kramaḥ kramāṇāmekaikaṃ prati pūrvāpara - kālayoḥ karttṛtvākarttṛtvāpatteḥ |",
    "2869:29": "2 . 2 evaṃ sarvakramābhāvāt kevalaṃ sakalakāryayaugapadyamavaśiṣyate |",
    "2869:30": "2 . 3 tatra ca sfuṭataraḥ pūrvāparakālayoḥ kattṛtvākarttṛtvaprasaṅgaḥ |",
    "2869:31": "2 . 4 virūddhe ca karttṛtvākarttṛtve ekadharmiṇi na sambhavataḥ |",
    "2869:32": "2 . 5 ekasvabhāvaśca tāvatkālamakṣaṇika iti siddha etasmin kramayaugapadyayorayogaḥ |",
    "2869:33": "2 . 6 tadevamakṣaṇike vyāpakānupalabdhyā niṣiddhaṃ sattvaṃ kṣaṇika evā [ va ] tiṣṭhate iti kṣaṇikatvena vyāptaṃ ( vyāptam ) |",
    "2869:34": "2 . 7 tattena vyāptaṃ yat yatra dharmiṇi sidhyati tatra kṣaṇikatvaṃ prasādhayati |",
    "2869:35": "2 . 8 idamevedānīṃ vicāryate |",
    "2869:36": "2 . 9 keyaṃ [ kveyaṃ ] vyāptirgrahītavyā dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇi sādhyadharmiṇi vā |",
    "2869:37": "2 . 10 kecidāhuḥ |",
    "2869:38": "2 . 11 dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇyeva dhūmavat |",
    "2869:39": "2 . 12 anyathā sādhanavaifalyaṃ syāt |",
    "2869:40": "2 . 13 ubhayadharmasiddhi [ ddhe ] ranāntarīyakatvāt vyāptisiddheḥ |",
    "2869:41": "2 . 14 nahi mahānasasiddhāyāmagnidhūmayorvyāptau punaragnisiddhaye dhūmaliṅgānviṣyata iti | 2 . 15 tathāhi |",
