    "2869:67": "none“> 4 . 0 pratyakṣadṛṣṭayorvahnidhūmayoḥ kāryakāraṇabhāvasiddhau tayorvyāptisiddhiriti pratyakṣasiddhe vahnau yuktamanumānavaifalyam |",
    "2869:68": "4 . 1 naivaṃ vyāptisiddheḥ prāk pramāṇāntarasiddhaṃ dharmiṇi kṣaṇikatvam |",
    "2869:69": "4 . 2 sādhanadharmameva tu kevalamanupaśyanto viparyyaye bādhakapramāṇabalāttasya kṣaṇikatvena vyāptiṃ pratīmaḥ |",
    "2869:70": "4 . 3 tattataḥ sādhanavaifalyam |",
    "2869:71": "4 . 4 vaifalyameva ,",
    "2869:72": "kṣaṇikatvavyāptasya sattvasya tathātvena dharmiṇi pratītau kṣaṇikatvasyāpi pratīteriti cet |",
    "2869:73": "4 . 5 na |",
    "2869:74": "4 . 6 sarvopasaṃhāravatī hi vyāptiḥ sādhyasiddheraṅgam |",
    "2869:75": "4 . 7 tadiyamanapekṣitadharmiviśeṣaṃ sādhanadharmamātramavalambate |",
    "2869:76": "4 . 8 tadyathā |",
    "2869:77": "4 . 9 yatra dhūmastatrāgniriti |",
    "2869:78": "4 . 10 na punaryatra mahānase dhūmastatrāgniriti |",
    "2869:79": "4 . 11 evamihāpi yat sattatkṣaṇikamiti vyāptipratītau sādhanadharmasyāpi dharmiṇi sattvaṃ nāntarbhavati |",
    "2869:80": "4 . 12 kiṃ punaḥ sādhyadharmasya |",
    "2869:81": "4 . 13 tasmāt sattvasāmānyasya sādhanadharmasya pakṣadharmatvaṃ vyāptiścaikaśaḥ pratipādya tadubhayasāmarthyāt sādhyadharmasya dharmiṇi vṛttiḥ pratīyata iti kuto'numānavaifalyaṃ ( kuto'numānavaifalyam ) |",
    "2869:82": "4 . 14 yadyevaṃ vyāptipratītāvasati dharmiṇi parāmarśe sādhyadharmiṇi vyāptigrahaṇamiti |",
    "2869:83": "4 . 15 kutaḥ |",
    "2869:84": "4 . 16 tatra dṛṣṭasya sattvasya vyāptipratīteḥ |",
    "2869:85": "4 . 17 yathā mahānasadṛṣṭāgnidhūmayorvyāptigrahe dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇi vyāptigrahaṇamucyate |",
    "2869:86": "4 . 18 na hi vyaptigrahaṇe mahānasaparāmarśo'stītyuktaṃ ( mahānasaparāmarśo'stītyuktam ) |",
    "2869:87": "4 . 19 nanu vyāptipakṣadharmatvayorekaśaḥ pratītāvapi yasyaiva pakṣadharmatvamavagatantasyaiva sādhyena vyāptiravasiteti sāmarthyāt sādhyasattākathanamavaiyarthyaṃ sādhanasya |",
    "2869:88": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2869:89": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2869:90": "none;text-autospace:none“>",
    "2869:91": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2869:92": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
    "2869:93": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2869:94": "none“> 5 . 0 nanu pakṣadharmatvagatiḥ sādhyagatiḥ sādhyadharmasaṃsparśāt |",
    "2869:95": "5 . 1 nāpi vyāptipratītireva sādhyasiddhiḥ |",
    "2869:96": "5 . 2 sāmānyālambanatayā dharmiviśeṣeṇa dharmayoranavacchedāt |",
    "2869:97": "5 . 3 anyathā viśeṣayorvyāpti prasaṅgāt tadayaṃ vyastaviṣayaḥ samarthyāditi hetunirddeśaḥ |",
    "2869:98": "5 . 4 atha hetostrairūpyaparicchedasāmarthyāt sādhyapratītirūtpadyate ityucyate |",
    "2869:99": "5 . 5 na tahīṃdānīṃ vyarthohetuḥ |",
    "2869:100": "5 . 6 svarūpaniścayena sādhyaniścayopajananāt |",
    "2869:101": "5 . 7 na hi kvacidiyattādhikaṃ liṅgasya karttavyamastīti |",
