    "2869:107": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2869:108": "none“> 6 . 0 api ca gṛhīte pakṣadharmatve sambandhe ca smṛte anumānaṃ bhavadbhiriṣyate |",
    "2869:109": "6 . 1 tadvadantarvyāptāvapīṣyatāṃ ( tadvadantarvyāptāvapīṣyatām ) |",
    "2869:110": "6 . 2 na hi bahirvyāptivādināmapi vismṛtāyāṃ vyāptau anumānapravṛttirasti |",
    "2869:111": "6 . 3 tatra yasyaiva pakṣadharmatvamavagataṃ tasyaiva sādhyadharmeṇa vyāptismṛteḥ kinna sarvānumānavaiyarthyaṃ ( sarvvānumānavaiyarthyam ) |",
    "2869:112": "6 . 4 sādhyadharmiṇo'parāmarśeṇa vyāpteḥ smaraṇāditi cet |",
    "2869:113": "6 . 5 sādhyadharmiṇi dṛṣṭasyaiva vyāptismaraṇe kathaṃ sādhyadharmiṇo'parāmarśaḥ |",
    "2869:114": "6 . 6 sāmānyalambanatvādvyāpteḥ |",
    "2869:115": "6 . 7 sādhyadharmiṇo'navacchedāditi cet |",
    "2869:116": "6 . 8 nanu tatra dṛṣṭasya kathaṃ tenānavacchedaḥ |",
    "2869:117": "6 . 9 tenāvacchinnasya vā asādhāraṇatvāt kathaṃ vyāptiḥ |",
    "2869:118": "6 . 10 ayogavyavacchedena viśeṣaṇānnāsādhāraṇateti cet |",
    "2869:119": "6 . 11 tathāpi kinna sādhyadharmī parāmṛśyate |",
    "2869:120": "6 . 12 yatra yatra parvate dhūmastatra tatrāgniryathā mahānasa iti sāmānyālambanāyāṃ vyāptau dharmiviśeṣa parāmarśasyānaṅgatvāditi cet yuktametat sādhyadharmiṇā hyayogavyavacchedaḥ sādhanadharmasya rūpāntarameva pakṣadhammatvākhyaṃ ( pakṣadharmatvākhyam ) |",
    "2869:121": "6 . 13 na tvayaṃ vyāpteraṅgaṃ ( vyāpteraṅgam ) |",
    "2869:122": "6 . 14 tamantareṇāpi vyāpteḥ sāmānyalambanāyāḥ paricchedaparisamāpteḥ kathamanyathā dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇi vyāptigrahaṇavārttāpi tadedānīṃ pakṣadharmatvāyogāt pakṣadharmatvāgrahaṇāt ;",
    "2869:123": "pakṣadharmatvagrahaṇe vā tadaiva sādhyamapi sāmarthyādasiddhaṃ siddhamiti sarvānumānavaiyarthyaprasaṅgaḥ |",
    "2869:124": "6 . 15 paścātkālabhāviliṅgajñānamapi ca smṛtireva syāt na pramāṇaṃ ( pramāṇam ) |",
    "2869:125": "6 . 16 tasmāt vyāpteranaṅgatvāt pakṣadharmatvaṃ vyāptigrahaṇe sadapi nāntarbhavatīti pṛthaggṛhītasmṛtayoḥ pakṣadharmatvavyāptyoḥ sāmarthyādanumeyagatirūtpadyate iti |",
    "2869:126": "6 . 17 evamavaiyarthyaṃ sādhanānāmeṣitavyam iti mānafalatvāt |",
    "2869:127": "6 . 18 tadvat pṛthagbhūtayoḥ pakṣadharmatvavyāptyoḥ sāmarthyādanumānotpattirantarvyāptāvapi kinneṣyate |",
    "2869:128": "6 . 11 tadiṣṭau vā kathaṃ sādhanavaiyarthyaṃ ( sādhanavaiyarthyam ) |",
    "2869:129": "6 . 20 trairūpyagatisāmarthyādanumeyagatiriti hi tadupādānaśaktireva sāmarthyamucyate ,",
    "2869:130": "na tu trairūpyapratīterantarbhāva iti sarvaṃ samānaṃ ( samānam ) |",
    "2869:131": "6 . 21 na sarvaṃ samānaṃ ( samānam ) |",
    "2869:132": "6 . 22 antarvyāptau hi vyāptiṃ prati gatyaiva pakṣadharmatvamavagataṃ anavagate pakṣadharmatve vyāpterapyanavagateḥ |",
    "2869:133": "6 . 23 tato vyāptipūrvake sādhanavāhye pakśadharmavacanamanarthakamanantavyāptau ( pakṣadharmavacanamanarthakamantarvyāptau ) |",
    "2869:134": "6 . 24 naivaṃ bahirvyāptau bahireva vyāptigrahaṇāt | 7 . 0 atrāha -",
