    "2869:175": "none“> 7 . 4 sūcitayo'stu tayoḥ sattve hetau prathamatarapakṣadharmatvaviṣayameva pramāṇamabhimukhībhavatu |",
    "2869:176": "7 . 5 tena pramāṇena dharmiṇi siddhasya sattvasya paścādvyāptiḥ pramāṇāntareṇa gṛhyata iti kasya vaiyarthyamiti |",
    "2869:177": "7 . 6 pratyakṣe'pi dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇi prathamaṃ heturgṛhyate paścādvyāptirityeṣa eva kramaḥ anyathā dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇi vyāptirgṛhītetyetadeva na syāt |",
    "2869:178": "7 . 7 dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇyadṛṣṭasyaiva hetorvyāptigrahaṇāt |",
    "2869:179": "7 . 8 yadyevaṃ sādhyadharmo'pi vyāptigrahaṇādhikaraṇe dharmiṇi grahītavya eva yathā vahnidhūmayoriti cet |",
    "2869:180": "7 . 9 na |",
    "2869:181": "7 . 10 tatra dṛṣṭasya hetorvipakṣe bādhakavṛttimādeva vyāptisiddheḥ |",
    "2869:182": "7 . 11 jñātaścaivaṃ na khalu vyāptigrahaṇāt prāk kṣaṇikasya kvacidapi siddhirasti tasyānumeyatvāt |",
    "2869:183": "7 . 12 asiddhāyāñca vyāptāvanumānāpravṛtteḥ |",
    "2869:184": "7 . 13 asiddhāyāñca vyāptāvanumānāpravṛtteḥ |",
    "2869:185": "7 . 13 sādhanāntarasya ca tadarthamananusaraṇāt |",
    "2869:186": "7 . 14 anusaraṇe'pyanavasthā syāt |",
    "2869:187": "7 . 15 avasthāne tāvat prayāsasya vaiyarthyāt |",
    "2869:188": "7 . 16 viparyyaye vyāptibalādeva vyāptisiddheravighātāt |",
    "2869:189": "7 . 17 vahnidhūmayostu nādṛṣṭayoḥ kāryakāraṇabhāvasiddheḥ |",
    "2869:190": "7 . 18 tatsiddhau na vipakṣe bādhakavṛttiriti dvayadarśanavyapekṣā vahnidhūmayorvyāptisiddhiḥ |",
    "2869:191": "7 . 19 sattvakṣaṇikatvayostu naivaṃ ( naivam ) |",
    "2869:192": "7 . 20 yathoktanyāyena vyāptisiddheḥ |",
    "2869:193": "7 . 21 tasmāt sattvamātrasya tatra dharmiṇi siddhasya bādhakavaśādvyāptiḥ setsyatītyeṣitavyaṃ ( setsyatītyeṣitavyam ) |",
    "2869:194": "7 . 22 tadvadantarvyāptāvapi |",
    "2869:195": "7 . 23 te ime vyāptipakṣadharmatve svasvapramāṇavyavaccha ( che )",
    "2869:196": "dyasādhanavākye na tu kevalaṃ sūcayitavye |",
    "2869:197": "7 . 24 na cānyataravākyena śakyamubhayaṃ sūcayitumiti kuto'nyataravākyavaiyarthyaṃ ( vaiyarthyam ) |",
