    "2869:230": "none“> 8 . 1 yadi hi dharmiṇi vyāptiḥ sidhyantyeva sādhyasiddhimantarbhāvayati |",
    "2869:231": "8 . 2 nanu lābha evaiṣaḥ |",
    "2869:232": "8 . 3 vyāptiprasādhakādeva pramāṇāt sādhyasiddheḥ sattvahetvapāśrayaṇaprayāsasya nirasanāt |",
    "2869:233": "8 . 4 na hi vyasanamevaitalliṅgāntarānusaraṇaṃ nāma |",
    "2869:234": "8 . 5 atha na vyāptisādhakāt sādhyasiddhiḥ |",
    "2869:235": "8 . 6 na tarhyanyarvyāptau hetuvaiyarthamiti kimakāṇḍakātaratayā bahutaramāyāsamāviśasi |",
    "2869:236": "8 . 7 dvayaṃ hi bhavataḥ sādhyaṃ dṛṣṭāntadharmiṇi vṛttiḥ sādhyadharmiṇi ca yathākramaṃ vyāptipakṣadharmatvayoḥ siddhayarthaṃ ( siddhayartham ) |",
    "2869:237": "8 . 8 nanu yadā pratiniyate dharmiṇi vivādaḥ ,",
    "2869:238": "tadvahirbhūte ca dharmiṇi vyāptigrahaṇaṃ tadānīṃ bhavedvaiyarthyaṃ ( bhavedvaiyarthyam ) |",
    "2869:239": "8 . 9 yadā tu vastumātre vivādaḥ tadā sarvvavastuṣu hetorvṛttistvayāpi sādhyā mayāpi ceti katamasmin dharmiṇi hetorvṛttisādhanaṃ mama vyarthaṃ bhaviṣyati |",
    "2869:240": "8 . 10 kathamidānīṃ bahirvyāptirvivādādhikaraṇaṃ bhūta evānyatamasmin vyāptisādhanāt |",
    "2869:241": "8 . 11 tāvanmātralakṣaṇatvācca sādhyadharmiṇaḥ |",
    "2869:242": "8 . 12 bādhakaṃ pramāṇaṃ pravarttamānamantargatamapi dharmiṇaṃ bahiṣkarotīti cet etadeva kathaṃ bhavatu bādhakena pravarttamānenaiva tasmin sādhyasādhanāt |",
    "2869:243": "8 . 13 sādhya saṃśayopagame sādhyadharmiṇi lakṣaṇopagamāditi cet ayuktametat |",
    "2869:244": "8 . 14 bādhakamātrāt na sādhyasiddhirityasmin pakṣe dharmyantaraparigrahavaiyarthyābhidhānāt |",
    "2869:245": "8 . 15 bādhakāt sādhyasiddhirityasmistu pakṣe sādhanavaiyarthyamāpāditaṃ ( sādhanavaiyarthyamāpāditam ) |",
    "2869:246": "8 . 16 tasmādvādhakamātreṇa sādhyāsiddhau na kvacit sandehanivṛttiḥ |",
    "2869:247": "8 . 17 sandehānivṛttau na bahiṣkaraṇamavahiṣkṛtaśca sādhyadharmyeveti tatra vyāptirantarvyāptireva nedānīṃ bahirvyāptervārttāpi |",
    "2869:248": "8 . 18 tadiyaṃ bahirvyāptiramusmin pakṣe kathaṃ bhavati |",
    "2869:249": "8 . 19 yadi pratiniyate dharmiṇi vivādaḥ tadvahirbhūte ca dharmiṇi vyāptigrahaṇambhavati |",
    "2869:250": "8 . 20 tatra ca durūddharaḥ dharmmyantaraparigrahavaiyarthyadoṣaḥ |",
    "2869:251": "8 . 21 bādhakamātreṇa tu sādhyasiddhau hetyantarameva vyarthaṃ ( vyartham ) |",
    "2869:252": "8 . 22 api ca satvahetorviśeṣeṇa na vahirvyāptisambhavaḥ |",
