    "2869:273": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2869:274": "none“> 8 . 24 yatra hi dharmiṇi dṛṣṭasya hetorvyāptiḥ pratīyate tatra tasya vyāptigrahaṇamākhyāyate |",
    "2869:275": "8 . 25 dṛṣṭañca sādhyadharmiṇi sattvamanyathā vimatyayogāditi kathaṃ nāntarvyāptiḥ |",
    "2869:276": "normal;mso-pagination:",
