    "2869:342": "atadyuktaścāsapakṣa iti |",
    "2869:343": "10 . 3 tasmin sapakṣa eva sattvamasapakṣe cāsattvameva yathākramamanvayavyatirekau tau punaryatra tatra vā dharmiṇi grahītavyau yatra śakyau grahītum |",
