    "2869:349": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2869:350": "none“> 10 . 4 tadiha sattvasya sarvato'kṣaṇikādvyāvṛttau bādhakabalāt siddhāyāṃ yat sattat kṣaṇikameveti anvayaḥ sādhyadharmiṇyavagṛhyate |",
    "2869:351": "10 . 5 tatra dṛṣṭasya hetorvyāptigrahaṇāt dharmyantarāsambhavāt |",
    "2869:352": "10 . 6 sambhave'pi tadanusaraṇavaiyarthyāt |",
    "2869:353": "10 . 7 yadyevamasādhāraṇo nāma kathamanai - kāntika uktaḥ | |",
