    "2869:370": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2869:371": "none“> 11 . 1 uktametajjaḍadhiyo dharmyantara eva vyāptigrahaṇaṃ pratipannāḥ |",
    "2869:372": "11 . 2 tadabhimānāpekṣayā'sādhāraṇamanaikāntikamāha śrāvaṇatvaṃ dṛṣṭāntābhāvāt |",
    "2869:373": "11 . 3 sādhyadharmiṇi ca vyāptiraniṣṭeragṛhītāyāṃ vyāptau sandigdhobhayatayā' niścayakaratvāt |",
    "2869:374": "11 . 4 athavā asādhāraṇataiva śrāvaṇatvasya mūdābhimānopakalpitā |",
    "2869:375": "11 . 5 dṛṣṭaiva hi śabdavyakti dharmiṇī vivādādhikaraṇāt |",
    "2869:376": "11 . 6 anyathā dharmyasiddhiprasaṅgācca |",
    "2869:377": "11 . 7 dṛṣṭādṛṣṭaśabdavyaktisādhāraṇañca śrāvaṇatvaṃ hetuḥ |",
    "2869:378": "11 . 8 dhūmasāmānyavat |",
    "2869:379": "11 . 9 tataḥ sarvopasaṃhāravatyāḥ vyāpteḥ sambhavāt sattvādivadadṛṣṭameva sādhanaṃ śrāvaṇatvākhyaṃ ( śrāvaṇatvākhyam ) |",
    "2869:380": "11 . 10 kramayaugapadyānupalambha eva cātra bādhakaṃ pramāṇaṃ ( pramāṇam ) |",
    "2869:381": "11 . 11 śrotrajñānajanakatvameva hi śrāvaṇatvaṃ ( śrāvaṇatvam ) |",
    "2869:382": "11 . 12 tasmānmūdavyapekṣayā'sādhāraṇatvāt |",
    "2869:383": "11 . 13 asādhāraṇasya sarvopasaṃhārāyogāt |",
    "2869:384": "11 . 14 sādhyadharmiṇi vyāptipratītāveva sādhyapratīteḥ sādhanavaifalyaṃ syādeva |",
    "2869:385": "11 . 15 tanmābhūdvaifalyamiti naivaṃ vyāptirgrahītavyā |",
    "2869:386": "11 . 16 tasyāmagṛhītāyāṃ sandigdhobhayatayā syādanaikāntikatvaṃ ( syādanaikāntikatvam ) |",
    "2869:387": "11 . 17 sarvopasaṃhāreṇa tu vyāptigrahaṇe yathoktanyāyena sādhanavaifalyābhāvāt |",
    "2869:388": "11 . 18 aduṣṭaṃ sattvādi sādhanameveti veditavyam |",
    "2869:389": "11 . 19 tadevamubhayathā mūdajanāpekṣayā'sādhāraṇamanaikāntikamuktam |",
